{"type": "article", "id": 29069, "title": "花园椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T05:10:59Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160704025239l6KVwH2QSdTZLjYO.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">喜欢条纹和缤纷的色彩？<a href=\"http://www.matalicrasset.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matali Crasset</a> 为法国的花园家具制造商 <a href=\"http://www.fermob.com/fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fermob</a> 设计的 Stripe 花园椅会让你眼前一亮：一改传统座椅采用的垂直放置的设计，Crasset 将铝制的拉伸板纵向放置，就像是一条优雅的曲线从上至下延伸，仿佛为座椅覆盖上了柔软的织物，提高了舒适性。Stripe 有一系列明亮鲜艳的色彩可选，能够为各类室外或者室内环境增添不一样的活力。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704025312xPzKS6pqQbTH3cwn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.322263\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704025401ToX0U76JkiFmSvnH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704025425zAYsTx3kXRa9iUVv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704025500tomVJYbpWqDZx2vj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}